Dominik Nowicki (1926-) was born a male in 1926, while his mother was on a carousel, he was born in Krakow, Poland on November 26th, 1926. His mothers name is Iga Nowicki, a flight attendant (age 20), his father was unknown as he passed before he was born.

== Early life ==
At age 4, he proceeded to tell a joke, getting some laughs in the crowd. At age 7, he started Little Gorski Primary School. At age, 10 he suffered from the common cold.
